\section{Effect of spatially localized fields}

\subsection{Gaussian fields}\label{sgaussian}

To study the effect of spatially localized out-of-plane fields on the gyrotropic frequency, we first consider centralized fields with a two-dimensional (2D) Gaussian-like profile:
